Package spx.packets.tracks

Provides definitions for SPx track packets.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExtendedFlags
    Defines bit flags for the optional fields in the Extended track report.
    Flags
    Defines bit flags for the flags field of Minimal track reports.
    Status
    Values for the status field in Minimal track packets.
    ThreatLevel
    Values for the level field in the Threat structure that is contained within extended track reports.
    ThreatType
    Values for the type field in the Threat structure that is contained within extended track reports.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Extended
    Extended track report.
    Fusion
    Fusion information.
    Minimal
    Minimal track reports.
    Normal
    Normal track reports.
    Secondary
    Secondary information.
    Sensor
    Defines bit flags for the sensor types use within the Fusion and Secondary reports contained within Extended track reports.
    Threat
    Threat information.

Package spx.packets.tracks Description

Provides definitions for SPx track packets. (e.g. for network transmission etc.)
